m_q.target_metric: Count of award-winning films where the opening film is 'Encounters at the End of the World'
filters: Opening Film = 'Encounters at the End of the World'
sub_questions: Which year had 'Encounters at the End of the World' as opening film?
What is the award-winning film for that year?
Is there exactly one matching record?

scale_issues: 'Number of Screening' column contains combined film and televised counts as text
Date columns are stored as text objects

format_notes: First column appears to be index column
Date columns contain month and day information
Opening Film column contains film titles, some with commas requiring quotes

constraints: Each row represents one festival year
Opening Film should be unique per year
Award-Winning Film should be unique per year
derived_filters: Year = 2008 (based on data sample showing 'Encounters at the End of the World' in 2008)
statistical_tests: Check if exactly one row matches the filter condition
